OL,3,CDoctor tells murder trial boy's burns
OL,4,Clooked like 'inflicted injury'
OL,6,FA three-year-old boy had suffered such
OL,7,Fextensive burns "he should have been
OL,8,Fadmitted to a burns unit" in the weeks
OL,9,Fbefore his alleged murder, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FChristina Robinson is accused of
OL,13,Fcausing a fatal head injury to her son
OL,14,FDwelaniyah at the family home in Ushaw
OL,15,FMoor, near Durham, in November 2022.
OL,17,FThe 30-year-old is also accused of
OL,18,Fdeliberately scalding his legs and
OL,19,Fbuttocks and hitting him with a bamboo
OL,20,Fcane.
